OL,3,CInheritance tax change 'a real threat
OL,4,Cto farming industry' in Wales
OL,6,FWelsh farmers have described the
OL,7,Fproposed changes to inheritance tax
OL,8,Frules laid out in the UK Government
OL,9,Fbudget as a "betrayal".
OL,11,FChancellor Rachel Reeves' changes mean
OL,12,Ffarms worth more than #1million will
OL,13,Fnow be subject to inheritance tax.
OL,15,FFrom April 2026 farmers will only be
OL,16,Fable to claim a 100% relief from
OL,17,Finheritance tax on the first #1million
OL,18,Fof combined agricultural and business
OL,19,Fassets, falling to 50% beyond that.
