OL,3,CInheritance tax change 'a real threat
OL,4,Cto farming industry' in Wales
OL,6,FShe said the #1million band would help
OL,7,Fprotect small farms, but a group
OL,8,Frepresenting landowners has described
OL,9,Fthe decision as a "betrayal".
OL,11,FFor years, the APR (Agricultural
OL,12,FProperty Relief) has enabled small
OL,13,Ffamily farms to be handed down over
OL,14,Fgenerations with some agricultural
OL,15,Fproperty free of inheritance tax.
OL,17,FAccording to the Country Land and
OL,18,FBusiness Association, the average farm
OL,19,Fasset in Wales in #1.8m, but the
OL,20,Faverage farm business income dropped
OL,21,Fto #24,000 this year per family.
