OL,3,CInheritance tax change 'a real threat
OL,4,Cto farming industry' in Wales
OL,6,FTom Homfray, vice-president of the
OL,7,FCLA, said the move had "caused a huge
OL,8,Famount of concern".
OL,10,F"Lots of family farms will be
OL,11,Fprofoundly affected by this," he told
OL,12,FITV Cymru Wales. "A huge number of
OL,13,Ffarms in Wales are valued on paper in
OL,14,Fexcess of #1m, but by no means does
OL,15,Fthat mean the farmers farming them
OL,16,Fhave access to the funds to pay a
OL,17,Fpotential tax liability.
