OL,3,CInheritance tax change 'a real threat
OL,4,Cto farming industry' in Wales
OL,6,F"It's a real threat to the industry,
OL,7,Fit's a real threat to family-owned
OL,8,Ffarms and it could lead to the
OL,9,Ffragmentation of a lot of these farms
OL,10,Fwhich people have been farming for
OL,11,Fgenerations."
OL,13,FThe CLA claims that, by its initial
OL,14,Fcalculations, the average farm in
OL,15,FWales will have to sell 10-15% of its
OL,16,Fland to fund the APR. They say this
OL,17,Fdoes not account for limited companies
OL,18,For other structures.
