OL,3,CInheritance tax change 'a real threat
OL,4,Cto farming industry' in Wales
OL,6,FLlinos Medi, Plaid Cymru MP for Ynys
OL,7,FMon, said Reeves' move to apply
OL,8,Finheritance tax to family farms will
OL,9,Fseriously threaten the rural economy
OL,10,Fin Wales.
OL,12,F"I am afraid that changes to rules on
OL,13,Finheritance will seriously threaten
OL,14,FWelsh family farms which are the
OL,15,Fbackbone of the rural economy," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
