OL,3,CInheritance tax change 'a real threat
OL,4,Cto farming industry' in Wales
OL,6,FVictoria Bond, director CLA Cymru
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is not a tax that affects
OL,8,Fa few 'rich' landowners as suggested
OL,9,Fby the Chancellor. It is a tax that
OL,10,Fstrikes at the heartland of Wales,
OL,11,Fimpacting the farms and communities
OL,12,Fthat are essential to our rural
OL,13,Feconomy.
