OL,3,CInheritance tax change 'a real threat
OL,4,Cto farming industry' in Wales
OL,6,F"Most Welsh farms are generational,
OL,7,Fwith families committed to sustaining
OL,8,Fthe land, rather than seeing it as a
OL,9,Frealisable asset. This policy could
OL,10,Fforce families to make impossible
OL,11,Fchoices and risks the future of Welsh
OL,12,Ffarming and the communities it
OL,13,Fsupports."
OL,15,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"Inheritance tax is a reserved tax,
OL,17,Foverseen by the UK Government. We will
OL,18,Fbe making our spending decisions as we
OL,19,Fdevelop our Draft Budget in the weeks
OL,20,Fahead. It will be published next
OL,21,Fmonth."
